co he recorded  points on for shooting from the field overall and added five assists and three rebounds in  minutes of action in the usas – exhibition game victory on august  in new york he was also named to the  usa senior national team on april   nba career statistics legend   gp games played   gs  games started  mpg  minutes per game  fg  field goal percentage  p  point field goal percentage  ft  free throw percentage  rpg  rebounds per game  apg  assists per game  spg  steals per game  bpg  blocks per game  ppg  points per game  bold  career high  led the league regular season year team gp gs mpg fg p ft rpg apg spg bpg ppg – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – philadelphia            – denver            – denver            – denver            – detroit            – memphis            – philadelphia            career            allstar            playoffs year team gp gs mpg fg p ft rpg apg spg bpg ppg  philadelphia             philadelphia             philadelphia             philadelphia             philadelphia             philadelphia             denver             denver            career            personal life iverson and rap star nelly at a reebok photoshoot during the  offseason iverson and his friends were stopped by a police officer for speeding late at night and was arrested for carrying a concealed weapon and for possession of marijuana he pleaded no contest and was sentenced to community service during the  offseason iverson recorded a rap single called  bars however after being criticized for its controversial lyrics he eventually was unable to release it going under his moniker jewelz the album was alleged to have made derogatory remarks about homosexuals after criticism from activist groups and nba commissioner david stern he agreed to change the lyrics but ultimately never released the album in august  he married his high school sweetheart tawanna at the mansion on main street in voorhees new jersey in  iverson was alleged to have thrown tawanna out of their home after a domestic dispute and later threatening two men with a gun while looking for her all charges against him were later dropped after the judge cited lack of evidence with contradictory statements from witnesses on february   iverson urinated in a trash can at ballys atlantic city casino and was told by casino management not to return on december   after the sixers defeated the charlotte bobcats iverson paid a latenight visit to the trump taj mahal after winning a hand at a threecardstud poker table iverson was overpaid  in chips by a dealer when the dealer quickly realized the mistake and requested the chips back iverson refused and a heated headturning argument between him and casino staff began atlantic city casino regulations reportedly state that when a casino makes a payout mistake in favor of the gambler he or she must return the money that they did not legitimately win by playing also in  iversons bodyguard jason kane was accused of assaulting a man at a washington d c nightclub after the man marlin godfrey refused to leave the clubs vip section so iversons entourage could enter godfrey suffered a concussion a ruptured eardrum a burst blood vessel in his eye a torn rotator cuff cuts and bruises and emotional distress although iverson did not touch godfrey himself godfrey sued iverson for the injuries caused by his bodyguard in  a jury awarded godfrey  the united states court of appeals for the district of columbia circuit upheld the verdict in  on march   iversons wife filed for divorce seeking custody of their five children as well as child support and alimony payments in august  an ohio man sued iverson for  million in damages claiming he was assaulted by iversons security guard in a  bar fight in detroit the federal judge dismissed the case finding no evidence that iverson or his bodyguard struck the plaintiff guy walker on may   iverson appeared on cbs this morning in support of a showtime network documentary on his life during which he addressed longdiscussed rumors of financial struggles denying any notion that he was struggling thats a myth thats a rumor the fact that im struggling in any part of my life he said awards and honors main article list of career achievements by allen iverson hall of famer class of  – individual nba most valuable player –  fourtime nba scoring champion time nba allstar twotime nba allstar game mvp time allnba threetime nba steals leader nba rookie of the year  number  retired by the philadelphia ers filmography like mike  – as himself imagine that  – as himself my other home  see also national basketball association portal list of national basketball association career scoring leaders list of national basketball association career free throw scoring leaders list of national basketball association career assists leaders list of national basketball association career steals leaders list of national basketball association career turnovers leaders list of national basketball association career minutes played leaders list of national basketball association players with most points in a game list of national basketball association players with most steals in a game list of national basketball association singlegame playoff scoring leaders list of national basketball association annual scoring leaders list of national basketball association annual minutes leaders references  lynn burke  september     allen iverson dailypresscom retrieved    a b allen iverson georgetown basketball history december   retrieved november     special dime greatest shooting guards of all time espn march   archived from the original on march     iverson at peace as he retires from basketball nbacom turner sports interactive inc october   retrieved october     naismith mem