must return the money that they did not legitimately win by playing also in  iversons bodyguard jason kane was accused of assaulting a man at a washington d c nightclub after the man marlin godfrey refused to leave the clubs vip section so iversons entourage could enter godfrey suffered a concussion a ruptured eardrum a burst blood vessel in his eye a torn rotator cuff cuts and bruises and emotional distress although iverson did not touch godfrey himself godfrey sued iverson for the injuries caused by his bodyguard in  a jury awarded godfrey  the united states court of appeals for the district of columbia circuit upheld the verdict in  on march   iversons wife filed for divorce seeking custody of their five children as well as child support and alimony payments in august  an ohio man sued iverson for  million in damages claiming he was assaulted by iversons security guard in a  bar fight in detroit the federal judge dismissed the case finding no evidence that iverson or his bodyguard struck the plaintiff guy walker on may   iverson appeared on cbs this morning in support of a showtime network documentary on his life during which he addressed longdiscussed rumors of financial struggles denying any notion that he was struggling thats a myth thats a rumor the fact that im struggling in any part of my life he said awards and honors main article list of career achievements by allen iverson hall of famer class of  – individual nba most valuable player –  fourtime nba scoring champion time nba allstar twotime nba allstar game mvp time allnba threetime nba steals leader nba rookie of the year  number  retired by the philadelphia ers filmography like mike  – as himself imagine that  – as himself my other home  see also national basketball association portal list of national basketball association career scoring leaders list of national basketball association career free throw scoring leaders list of national basketball association career assists leaders list of national bask